## Ingredients

- 3 tbsp Olive oil
- 2 tsp minced garlic
- 2 big bags spinach
- 1 can Sun dried tomatoes
- 1/2-3/4 cup Sour Cream
- 2-4 oz goat cheese Goat Cheese
- Pasta
- Salt and pepper
- Parmesan, romano, asiago cheese blend

## Instructions

1. Boil Pasta
2. Heat olive oil in wok
3. Add garlic
4. Add spinach
5. Add S+P to taste
6. Add sun dried tomatoes
7. Add 3/4 cup of the hot pasta water
8. Add sour cream
9. Add goat cheese
10. Add the pasta
